title: 8 The Feast of the Drowned-Doctor Who-Stephen Cole ZEO
description:
The Feast of the Drowned is a BBC Books original novel written by Stephen Cole and based on the long-running British science fiction television series Doctor Who. It was published on April 13, 2006, alongside The Stone Rose and The Resurrection Casket. It features the Tenth Doctor, Rose and Mickey.

About The Author:
Stephen Cole(also credited as Steve Cole) is an English author of children's books and science fiction.Cole's most successful titles to date are the Astrosaurs children's books, published under the name Steve Cole.

File Formats: EPUB , MOBI , AZW3 , PDF
